		<h3>Rodco and the Sixth Framework</h3>
		<h4 class="subheader">A success story of a Market leader using "Sixth"</h4>
		
		<hr />
		
		<h4>What's in Sixth?</h4>
		<p>A framework for creating robust, maintainable business macro-applications hosted entirely on the cloud with affordable development and operating costs.</p>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="six columns">
				<ul>
					<li><h5>Salesforce.com (Force.com)</h5>Database , Security and Administrative Interfaces like Reporting and Listings. A business designed & programable platform used for creating process , workflows and react to changes in data. </li>
					<li><h5>Sinatra / Rails</h5>Standard based and robust Integration Hub; is the center of the system that allows mobile, tablet, offline and web applications to send and receive data with force.com.</li>
					<li><h5>Node-Js</h5>  The latest invention in software, a powerful server that is able to handle millions of simultaneous requests from intranet and customer facings apps. Is the power-horse behind beautiful and engaging web and mobile applications. </li>
				</ul>
				</div>
				
				<div class="six columns">
				<ul>
					<li><h5>Foundation</h5>A design framework for creating slick designs, with a hidden power. It helps build adaptable designs for desktop, tablets and mobiles phones; Increases production of application in ~400%.</li>
					<li><h5>SpineJs</h5>Makes applications responsive, entertaining and fast. A front-end (client side) framework for creating robust and maintainable apps in a fraction of the time.  </li>
					<li><h5>Sixth</h5>The glue that joins them all. Sixth is a set of patterns and procedures that makes each of the parts of a modern cloud hosted enterprise system perform as with the accuracy of the Space Shuttle. Standards based, 100% Open Source. </li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
		
